desc: Automatically sets a random Unsplash image as your wallpaper daily or manually.
doc:
Automatically sets a random Unsplash image as your wallpaper daily. Click on reload config to set a random wallpaper manually. 

 Load extension by adding hs.loadSpoon('UnsplashRandom') in your init.lua

Download: [https://github.com/Hammerspoon/Spoons/raw/master/Spoons/UnsplashRandom.spoon.zip](https://github.com/Hammerspoon/Spoons/raw/master/Spoons/UnsplashRandom.spoon.zip)
name: UnsplashRandom
